---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Our School" description="Learn about our ethos, school values, and staff.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container page-intro">
      <h1>Our School</h1>
      <p>
        Faugher National School is rooted in a warm and respectful school culture. We aim to provide a happy place to
        learn while helping each pupil to grow in confidence, ability, and character.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container grid-two">
      <article class="panel prose">
        <h2>Principal Welcome</h2>
        <p>
          As principal, it gives me great pleasure to welcome you to our school website. It is designed to offer a
          glimpse of the welcoming, fun, and happy environment that Faugher National School is known for.
        </p>
        <p>
          As you explore the site, you will find information about our ethos, achievements, and school updates. Please
          contact us if you need any further information. I look forward to meeting you in the near future.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="panel prose">
        <h2>Our Ethos</h2>
        <p>
          We promote kindness, inclusion, and high expectations for all pupils. Teaching and learning are planned to
          support each child at their own stage while encouraging curiosity, effort, and participation.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our school values positive home-school communication, active learning, and a safe environment where children
          feel known and supported.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container panel prose">
      <h2>Staff Overview</h2>
      <p>This section can be updated each year with current staffing information.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Principal</li>
        <li>Mainstream Class Teachers</li>
        <li>Special Education Team</li>
        <li>Special Needs Assistants</li>
        <li>Administrative and Support Staff</li>
      </ul>
      <p><a href="/classrooms">View Junior Room, Senior Room, and Achievements.</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
